               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420131-name-623" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420131-name-623" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420131-name-623" type="surname" value="PEASLEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420131-name-623" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>ELIZABETH PEASLEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of John Peasley, of Hemming's-buildings, Pentonville—I have a little child four years old. Between twelve and one o'clock in the afternoon of the 7th of January, I sent her on an errand with a cloak on—at ten minutes to two she was being brought back by two females against the turnpike at Islington—this is the cloak.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. ENDERGAST</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Are you sure it is your child's cloak? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes, I am positive—I had had it about a fortnight—I am not mistaken—there is no mark of my own upon it—I bought it of a housekeeper in Chapel-street—I never saw the prisoner till she was at the station.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420131-name-624" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420131-name-624" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420131-name-624" type="surname" value="WEIBLE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420131-name-624" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEIBLE</persName>
                  </hi>. I have produced the cloak—the prisoner sold it to me on the 8th of January.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> You have inquired into her circumstances? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes, she was in great distress—she and her mother were almost dying for want.</p>
               <p>
